Cash Flow Present value and IRR DetailThe calculation of present value is one of the basics of finance. The present value is the current value of a stream of future payments. The internal rate of return (IRR)of a cash flow is the interest rate that makes the present value of a cash flow equal to zero.The calculation of present value is one of the basics of finance. The present value is the current value of a stream of future payments.Present value,If discounting was discrete